defs.name: Error
defs.value:
pub enum Error {

    #[doc = r" Invalid compression pointer not pointing backwards"]
    #[doc = r" when parsing label"]
    BadPointer,

    #[doc = r" Packet is smaller than header size"]
    HeaderTooShort,

    #[doc = r" Packet ihas incomplete data"]
    UnexpectedEOF,

    #[doc = r" Wrong (too short or too long) size of RDATA"]
    WrongRdataLength,

    #[doc = r" Packet has non-zero reserved bits"]
    ReservedBitsAreNonZero,

    #[doc = r" Label in domain name has unknown label format"]
    UnknownLabelFormat,

    #[doc = r" Query type code is invalid"]
    InvalidQueryType(u16),

    #[doc = r" Query class code is invalid"]
    InvalidQueryClass(u16),

    #[doc = r" Type code is invalid"]
    InvalidType(u16),

    #[doc = r" Class code is invalid"]
    InvalidClass(u16),

    #[doc = r" Invalid characters encountered while reading label"]
    LabelIsNotAscii,

    #[doc = r" Invalid characters encountered while reading TXT"]
    TxtDataIsNotUTF8(Utf8Error),

    #[doc = r" Parser is in the wrong state"]
    WrongState,

    #[doc = r" Additional OPT record found"]
    AdditionalOPT,
}
